messages.message: Does that number seem low or high to you? Sounds quite plausible to me. Assuming 40 hours a week, which means 640 hours for the first 4 months, is 727 pages an hour. If there's 10 of us on average using Flow, then we have 72 pages an hour. Seems on the high side but possible
Flow v2 requires ocr always, so I could understand it... But everyone would have to turn pdf cache off + use force image ocr.
